@startuml
title ElectroCorp Web App - Frontend Bounded Contexts
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

class "IAM" as FrontendIAM <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Billing" as FrontendBilling <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Workplace" as FrontendWorkplace <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Device Control" as FrontendDeviceControl <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Energy Monitoring" as FrontendEnergyMonitoring <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Notifications" as FrontendNotifications <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Reporting" as FrontendReporting <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Service Management" as FrontendServiceManagement <<Bounded Context>> {}
class "Shared UI / Kernel" as FrontendSharedKernel <<Bounded Context>> {}

FrontendIAM ..> FrontendSharedKernel : guards / session / layout
FrontendBilling ..> FrontendIAM : authenticated customer
FrontendBilling ..> FrontendSharedKernel : plan access guard
FrontendWorkplace ..> FrontendSharedKernel : layout and state
FrontendWorkplace ..> FrontendDeviceControl : device assignment views
FrontendDeviceControl ..> FrontendEnergyMonitoring : device consumption context
FrontendDeviceControl ..> FrontendNotifications : alert rule targets
FrontendEnergyMonitoring ..> FrontendReporting : metrics for reports and goals
FrontendNotifications ..> FrontendSharedKernel : badges / toast feedback
FrontendReporting ..> FrontendSharedKernel : charts and cards
FrontendServiceManagement ..> FrontendWorkplace : location and device incidents
FrontendServiceManagement ..> FrontendSharedKernel : ticket UI primitives

@enduml
